sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as Alice (App)
    participant S as Server
    participant B as Bob (App)

    A->>A: ECDH X25519 + HKDF → shared key
    A->>A: AES-GCM encrypt(plaintext)
    A->>S: e2e-message {to: bob, payload: ciphertext}
    Note over S: relay — KHÔNG giải mã
    S->>B: forward ciphertext
    B->>B: decrypt → hiển thị UI → lưu SQLite
    Note over S: messagesStored = 0 (mặc định)
